								<h3>Illinois Business Innovation Services (BIS)</h3>
								<p>Helping thousands of organizations for over 30 years, the professionals at Illinois BIS specialize in customized training and consulting to help organizations improve performance with sustainable results.</p>
								<p>We also offer public courses and workshops at our Naperville Center to foster individual growth and knowledge.</p>
								<h5 style="font-size:18px;">Reputation Counts - Over 90% of our new customers are referred to us by current customers!</h5>
								<p>Our most effective role is to help develop the potential within each organization to achieve a culture where innovation and constant improvement thrive.</p>
								<p>Our hallmark has been our ability to help organizations grow profitably by collaborating with the talent within the organization.  We believe that people embrace what they help to create.</p>
								<p>We introduce new methodologies and tools and help organizations develop a focused, mission-driven culture designed to inspire ideas that create the future.</p>
								
								<!--
								<h3>Transition</h3>
								
								<p>Since 1983 BIS has provided outstanding customized training services that have helped our customers remain globally competitive primarily in Illinois.  BIS has been associated with the University of Illinois since 2006, but in recent years, it became apparent that BIS could gain flexibility and efficiency as a separate organization.  Therefore, BIS and U of I agreed to end their affiliation in December of 2015, and we are delighted with this transition.</p>
                                
